DAoC is gonna be my baby though!   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/uratdm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ratdm</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(7/3/01 3:51:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Ages of Camelot</span><hr size=1> Of course sb won't be item dependant..... And the dev team supposedly won't sit and tolerate hackers from what I've heard they will probably come down extremely hard on hacker and abusers because they have to.  And anybody who thinks that Daoc will be filled with good people who won't exploit isn't to realistic, yeah sb could get the crap of the crop but I wouldn't be suprised if daoc gets its fair share of griefers and l33t h4xx0rs <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>-Deluwen Blackguard
